58
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,430
What do you want?

59
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:30,300
Loyalty.

60
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:34,340
Loyalty...

61
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:37,060
Loyalty!

62
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:38,730
Loyalty?

63
00:05:40,220 --> 00:05:42,230
- Loyalty?
- Loyalty.

64
00:05:42,230 --> 00:05:46,170
I want to become your belief, everything that you believe in.

65
00:05:46,170 --> 00:05:52,560
I want you to give me all of your loyalty toward your friends, siblings, and everyone.

66
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,830
Impossible.

67
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:56,370
I can't give my loyalty up!

68
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:07,160
No one will refuse me.

69
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:10,650
I can let you live and be happy.

70
00:06:10,650 --> 00:06:12,540
Don't hesitate.

71
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,290
Submit to me.

72
00:06:14,290 --> 00:06:16,270
