213
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:15,570
Director of the Secretariat Wei Qiyang instead kept advising me

214
00:17:15,570 --> 00:17:18,230
to use this chance to obtain the crown prince position.

215
00:17:18,230 --> 00:17:22,850
This person was deliberately instigating conflict and his actions were of evil intentions.

216
00:17:22,850 --> 00:17:27,810
I got so enraged and immediately punished him on site.

217
00:17:27,810 --> 00:17:31,380
But Director of the Secretariat Wei holds office in the imperial court

218
00:17:31,380 --> 00:17:33,190
and respectfully earns imperial graces.

219
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:36,480
