234
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:38,410
Royal Sister-in-law.

235
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:40,750
Royal Sister-in-law.

236
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:50,790
Do you feel better?

237
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,930
Wuji.

238
00:18:53,490 --> 00:18:56,770
I want to see Wuji.

239
00:18:56,770 --> 00:18:59,560
Hurry and assist Empress up.

240
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:02,230
Your Majesty.

241
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:20,640
Take me to see Wuji, okay?

242
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:22,850
I beg you.

243
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:28,670
The journey to South Border is far and your body is weak.

244
00:19:28,670 --> 00:19:33,460
If anything bad happens to you, Wuji will not rest in peace, either.

245
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:36,370
My son is gone.

246
00:19:36,370 --> 00:19:40,830
I am unable to send him off on his last journey.

247
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:44,000
I'm unwilling to accept it.

248
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:52,070
Empress. Prince.

249
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:55,030
